text: Added the base texture for sheep.
The eyes on spiders now glow in the dark.
The slime texture has been updated.
Added textures for ghasts and zombie pigmen.
The zombie pigman's texture was changed, removing blood and adding thx xaphobia in the unused section for the final release.
Added the silverfish texture in preparation.
Added textures for cave spiders and endermen.
The pig texture has changed to accommodate for its new model.
Changes appear to have been made to the zombie texture. Its file size is different, however there appear to be no differences visually.
Added textures for blazes, magma cubes, mooshrooms, snow golems, and six villager professions.
Added an ender dragon texture called "ender". This is assumed to be the ender dragon's actual texture.
Added a texture for ender dragon eyes, and a texture named "shuffle" almost certaintly used for its death animation.
Updated many mob textures, likely due to UV changes on the rear.
Added textures for ocelots and cats.
Updated cow, mooshroom and sheep textures, likely to fix hooves.
The iron golem's texture has been resized as to be a power of two.
The zombie texture now includes a zombie villager head.
The zombie pigman texture is now 64x64.
The tamed wolf texture no longer has a collar attached.
Zombie villagers now have a unique texture.
As a result, the head has been removed from the original zombie texture, although it remains 64x64 and the head texture remains there with alpha 0.
Added a texture for wither skeletons.
Withers now have a unique invul texture.
Added textures for bats and witches.
The witch texture has been resized.
Six horse colors have been added.
Marking textures have been added, applied to horses for variation.
Skeleton and zombie horse textures have been added.
Donkey and mule textures have been added.
Certain horse textures have changed to solve an alignment issue.[1]
Steve's texture is now 64x64 and includes different opposite limb textures.
Added textures for guardians and elder guardians.
Added textures for cows and pigs retextured to horses.
Added textures for the pink wither.
The pink wither textures now outright replaces the wither textures.
Creepers and iron golems have been retextured for thematic purposes.
The arrow texture file has been updated to add purple skeleton arrows.
Added the fishing bobber texture, confusingly to particles.png.
Added the texture for experience orbs.
The experience orb texture now features more orb sizes.
The minecart texture has been adjusted slightly.
The item frame texture has been added (oddly, to terrain.png rather than as its own entity texture).
Added the texture for lead knots.

Added the arrow, spectral arrow and tipped arrow (identical to normal arrow) textures to a projectiles directory. The prior arrow texture still exists in the main entities folder, but is unused from this snapshot onwards.
The texture for shulker bullets is added.
The item frame texture has been updated.
Added obsidian boats with a dedicated texture.
Boats and minecarts have been retextured for thematic purposes.
Added the texture for the enchanting table's book.
Added the texture for end crystal beams.
The texture used for the crystal object/nether star within the beacon has been added.
The beacon's beam texture has been added.
The beacon beam texture has changed.
The beacon crystal texture has been removed, having no longer been used since 12w38a onwards.
Added a texture for the guardian's beam.
Added the texture of plate armor, worn by some mobs.
Added an unused chain armor texture.
Added a texture for sheep wool.
Added textures for gold, chainmail, iron and diamond armor sets.
Added the textures for leather armor.
Added a texture for saddles when worn by pigs.
Added the texure used by charged creepers.
Leather armor's base texture is now grayscale to allow for dyeing.
Wolf collars are now their own texture to allow for dyeing.
Leather and diamond chest armor texture sleeves have changed.
Added textures for regions on leather armor unaffected by dyeing.
Leather caps now have shading to support these regions and he nose guard has been removed.
Added the armor texture for the pink wither.
The pink wither armor texture now outright replaces the wither armor texture.
